_eval/](https://tatsu-lab.github.io/alpaca_eval/)\n8. [https://github.com/rasbt/LLMs-from-scratch/blob/main/ch07/01_main-chapter-code/instruction-data.json](https://github.com/rasbt/LLMs-from-scratch/blob/main/ch07/01_main-chapter-code/instruction-data.json)\n9. [https://github.com/openai/tiktoken](https://github.com/openai/tiktoken)\n10. [https://arxiv.org/abs/2405.14394](https://arxiv.org/abs/2405.14394)\n11. [https://huggingface.co/meta-llama/Meta-Llama-3-8B-Instruct](https://huggingface.co/meta-llama/Meta-Llama-3-8B-Instruct)\n12. [https://arxiv.org/pdf/2009.03300](https://arxiv.org/pdf/2009.03300)\n13. [https://drive.google.com/file/d/1OCpr4GZVmNNEXDpLuG2GZ1LlnJ_uvqPN/view?usp=sharing](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1OCpr4GZVmNNEXDpLuG2GZ1LlnJ_uvqPN/view?usp=sharing)\n14. [https://github.com/tatsu-lab/stanford_alpaca](https://github.com/tatsu-lab/stanford_alpaca)\n\n"